title: War of the Roses: She Wants a "Bang" Tattoo
description: Logan suspects her boyfriend is cheating on her and thinks she knows who he's cheating with.  That girl has a very specific tattoo so Logan tells her boyfriend she's going to get the same tattoo to see Logan's reaction but it didn't help figure out if he's cheating.  So now she needs War of the Roses to figure out what's going on!
